generated_text:
Sure, here is a sample promotional email in HTML format:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
       .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
       .header {
            text-align: center;
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
       .content {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
       .gift {
            background: #e0f7fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
       .gift img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
       .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
    <title>Your Reserved Gift</title>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Your Gift is Ready!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="gift">
            <h2>Congratulations! Your gift has been reserved for you.</h2>
            <img src="gift-image.jpg" alt="Reserved Gift">
            <p>Dear Valued Customer,</p>
            <p>We are excited to inform you that your gift has been successfully reserved and is ready for pickup. Here are the details:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Gift: {Your Gift Name}</li>
                <li>Pickup Date: {Pickup Date}</li>
                <li>Pickup Time: {Pickup Time}</li>
                <li>Location: {Pickup Location}</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We appreciate your business and look forward to seeing you soon!</p>
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p>The {Your Company Name} Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 {Your Company Name}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
```

